@node "introduction" "TrueReality - Introduction"

 This is a Nintendo 64 emulator for Amigas equiped with a PPC board.

@endnode

@node "requirements" "TrueReality - Requirements"

 Hardware:

  * Amiga 1200/3000/4000 with a PowerPC board
  * 32 MB of free RAM (more with large ROMs)
  * OS 3.0+

 Software:

  * WarpUP v4.0
  * CGFX v3 or later
  * StormMESA from H&P
  * lowlevel.library for CD32 pad support

@endnode

