@node "development" "TrueReality - Development"

 The TrueReality PPC Amiga port is developed using:

 v990203.x-v990216.2, A1300Ti -> 040/FPU/MMU'25, 603e'200, 2+128+0MB, AGA.
 v990322.1-           A1300Ti -> 040/FPU/MMU'25, 603e'200, 2+128+8MB, BVision.

@endnode

