@node "history" "TrueReality - History"

 990629.2 -000120
          -Some small fixes to this old version. There is actually a newer version of TR out,
           but since the static compiler isn't complete, there is no reason to update the Amiga
           version to that release. I've also ditched the 2D and J3D versions, after all, the
           N64 is a 3D consol, and no one likes playing a 3D game in wireframe!
          -The Mario64 logo is now visible after fixing an Amiga specific bug.
          -000123
          -Major graphical improvements. Mario 64 now looks a lot better!



@endnode
